---
import CoreLayout from '~/layouts/CoreLayout.astro'
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon'
---

<CoreLayout>
	<section class="relative w-full px-edge pt-32">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
			<div class="flex space-x-5">
				<div class="relative">
					<Image
						class="h-24 w-24 rounded-full object-cover"
						src={import('~/imgs/headshot-schneider.jpg')}
						alt="clayton schneider"
					/>
					<div
						class="absolute left-1/2 top-1/2 -z-10 h-[104px] w-[104px] -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 rounded-full bg-yellow-400"
					>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div>
					<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">Clayton Schneider</h1>
					<p class="mt-2">Full-Stack Developer Looking For Work</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<ul class="mt-5 flex space-x-4">
				<li class="">
					<a
						class="flex items-center space-x-1 text-slate-600"
						href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/clayton-schneider/"
						target="_blank"
					>
						<Icon name="mdi:linkedin" size={30} />
						<span class="font-bold">LinkedIn</span>
					</a>
				</li>
				<li class="">
					<a
						class="flex items-center space-x-1 text-slate-600"
						href="https://github.com/clayton-schneider"
						target="_blank"
					>
						<Icon name="mdi:github" size={30} />
						<span class="font-bold">Github</span>
					</a>
				</li>
			</ul>
			<div class="mt-5 space-y-2 leading-relaxed">
				<p>I love building and learning about software.</p>
				<p>
					I taught myself to code my junior year of college. While studing manufacturing engineering
					and business management I realized that my passion has always been to code. More
					specifically, how can we automate the boring and empower others to do more of what they
					love?
				</p>
				<p>
					My work experience at Carling Technologies, Slooh, and Simply Sprout has taught me many
					valuable lessons in front-end and back-end development. Collaborative and hard-working, I
					am not afraid to ask questions and always look for improvements.
				</p>
				<p>I am looking for a new developer position. Looking to hire?</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</CoreLayout>

<section class="px-edge py-10 lg:py-20">
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
		<div class="text-center lg:text-left">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">My Projects</h2>
			<p>Here are some projects that I am proud of:</p>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-20 flex flex-col items-center justify-between gap-10 lg:flex-row lg:items-start">
			<div class="max-w-xl text-center lg:text-left">
				<h3 class="text-3xl font-bold">I Cheat At Wordle</h3><p
					class="mt-2 text-lg leading-relaxed"
				>
					This tool will filter through all the five letter words in the english language and show
					you your remaining guesses so that you can win Wordle faster.
				</p>
				<div>
					<a
						target="_blank"
						class="text-primary mt-2 inline-block rounded border border-yellow-400 bg-yellow-400 px-8 py-1 font-bold"
						href="https://icheatatwordle.com"
						>View App
					</a>
					<a href="/projects/icheatatwordle">My Analysis</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div>
				<Image
					height={500}
					src={import('~/imgs/projects/icheatatwordle/icheatatwordle.png')}
					alt="I Cheat At Wordle"
				/>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
